metadata.description:
Hi! This is the “real value” nft! 
By purchasing this nft ring you get a real one that is made 1/1 for you from silver .925 and gold .999. 

The idea and cover was created by Srnk Sasha, Stepan Shechkov was responsible for the visuals and Nikita Ulanov is an author of the music.
